{"tid":342584,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)北韓生日節目","createTime":"2017-07-31T17:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T20:50:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea1c3d2522e1188192473de4e60f4864ff9bbf1","tid":342584,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=57acf1fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要入V台主頁先無左上舊野...<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c193bc64\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暫時解決方法睇住dailymotion或直接入V台個網睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYkwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=aca8a7f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4e/Your_name_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4e%2FYour_name_poster.jpg&h=91b3734e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img31.mtime.cn/mt/2014/02/22/232317.63272377_270X405X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg31.mtime.cn%2Fmt%2F2014%2F02%2F22%2F232317.63272377_270X405X4.jpg&h=9fc982cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.迪亞馬特彗星（ティアマト彗星）每逢1200年造訪地球，在深山小鎮糸守町（糸守町／いともりまち）[註 7]中家族世代經營鎮內「宮水神社」的高中少女宮水三葉、以及東京四谷[註 8]的高中少年立花瀧，從某天開始，在睡覺的時候，就會靈魂互換，醒來什麼都不記得，感覺像做了奇妙的夢，但周圍的人會講出他們昨天有違平常。他倆很快意識到這種情形，困惑之中開始在彼此智慧型手機留言，逐漸地變得習慣於身體切換，並干預對方的生活。三葉不僅樂於所嚮往的東京生活，也利用女人心這點..<br />\n<br />\n2.一個在夜總會演出的吉他手，他深愛的女友被冷血大毒梟殺害，左手被毒梟用槍射傷，無法繼續彈琴。他帶著攜滿武器的吉他琴盒在各鎮之間遊蕩， 為的是找到毒梟，待機報仇。大毒梟得到消息後，派手下去追殺他，在他身陷險境之際，一個美艷<br />\n<br />\n3.吉他手埃爾（安東尼奧班德拉斯 Antonio Banderas 飾）是墨西哥荒漠上最令人聞風喪膽的神槍手，他曾經摧毀了一個又一個當地的毒梟、黑幫，因此也八面樹敵。在痛失愛妻之後，心灰意冷的埃爾背著他的吉他開始四處流浪，從此銷聲匿跡。　　現今，大毒梟巴羅瑞（威廉達福 Willem Dafoe 飾）逐漸建立起了他的毒品王國，野心勃勃的他甚至還在密謀刺殺總統，推翻墨西哥政權。 CIA探員桑德斯（約翰尼德普 Johnny Depp 飾）得知了巴羅瑞的陰謀，於是，他找到了埃爾。曾經的鐵血戰士埃爾當然不會袖手旁觀，他終於重出江湖。但是，事情並沒有表面的那麼簡單，墨西哥荒漠上一出傳奇正在徐徐上演..<br />\n<br />\n1 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a29affc99cf2c6b45bca856194fb2047bbc9ec2","tid":342584,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T17:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a2f2e778016c5c93c57f185fa14a9a95079d96","tid":342584,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d325dcca0ad94aa71dc5b608df68b1a2390016","tid":342584,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T17:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f65e6adf94de35ab615cf22b68f49a419f91abc","tid":342584,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201